Package calculator

package calculator
  • Class
    Description
    AbstractCalculator
    Abstract base class for implementations of Calculator.
    AbstractCalculatorTest
    Tests for Calculators.
    AbstractCalculatorTest.SimpleCalculatorTest
    This class tests simple calculator.
    AbstractCalculatorTest.SmartCalculatorTest
    This class tests smart calculator.
    Calculator
    This interface represents a single calculator that supports two operations: take user input and returns current result of the calculator.
    SimpleCalculator
    A simple calculator takes straightforward inputs to perform computation between given operands and operator.
    SmartCalculator
    A smart calculator accepts inputs like simple calculator, and is backwards compatible with it.
